sequenceDiagram
    participant PO as Product Owner
    participant HUFile as HU-234 File
    participant HUPlan as hu-work-planner

    box Backend Team (Workflow 05)
    participant TDD as tdd-feature-developer
    participant TSBack as typescript-expert
    participant CodeRevBE as code-reviewer
    participant Arch as architect-review
    participant DebugBE as debugger
    end

    box Frontend Team (Workflow 03)
    participant Figma as Figma Design
    participant FigmaDev as figma-frontend-developer
    participant TSFront as typescript-expert
    participant CodeRevFE as code-reviewer
    participant MobileUX as mobile-ux-engineer
    participant DebugFE as debugger
    end

    box Integration & Deployment
    participant Int as Integration
    participant Deploy as hostinger-ssh-manager
    participant Prod as Production
    end

    %% PHASE 1: Planning
    Note over PO,HUPlan: PHASE 1: HU Analysis & Planning (1.5h)
    PO->>HUFile: Provide user story
    HUFile->>HUPlan: Read HU-234-payment-notifications.txt

    activate HUPlan
    Note right of HUPlan: - Parse requirements<br/>- Break down tasks<br/>- Estimate effort<br/>- Identify risks
    HUPlan-->>PO: Work plan with estimates (13h total)
    deactivate HUPlan

    %% PHASE 2: Backend Development
    Note over TDD,DebugBE: PHASE 2: Backend Development - TDD (6h)

    HUPlan->>TDD: Backend requirements
    activate TDD
    Note right of TDD: Write failing tests:<br/>- Unit tests<br/>- Integration tests<br/>- E2E API tests
    TDD->>TSBack: Tests written (failing)
    deactivate TDD

    activate TSBack
    Note right of TSBack: Implement:<br/>- DB schema<br/>- API endpoints<br/>- Business logic<br/>- WebSocket<br/>- Email service
    TSBack-->>CodeRevBE: Implementation complete
    deactivate TSBack

    activate CodeRevBE
    Note right of CodeRevBE: Review:<br/>- Security (OWASP)<br/>- Best practices<br/>- Error handling<br/>- Performance
    CodeRevBE-->>Arch: ✓ Code approved
    deactivate CodeRevBE

    activate Arch
    Note right of Arch: Validate:<br/>- SOLID principles<br/>- Layering<br/>- Scalability<br/>- Extensibility
    Arch-->>DebugBE: ✓ Architecture sound
    deactivate Arch

    activate DebugBE
    Note right of DebugBE: - Run all tests<br/>- Fix failures<br/>- Coverage >80%<br/>- Performance test
    DebugBE-->>Int: ✓ Backend ready
    deactivate DebugBE

    %% PHASE 3: Frontend Development
    Note over Figma,DebugFE: PHASE 3: Frontend Development - Figma (6h)

    HUPlan->>Figma: UI requirements
    Figma->>FigmaDev: Figma design file URL

    activate FigmaDev
    Note right of FigmaDev: Figma MCP:<br/>- get_file_data()<br/>- get_variables()<br/>- Extract tokens<br/>- Generate components
    FigmaDev->>TSFront: React components + types
    deactivate FigmaDev

    activate TSFront
    Note right of TSFront: TypeScript:<br/>- Interfaces<br/>- Props types<br/>- Hooks<br/>- WebSocket client
    TSFront-->>CodeRevFE: Type-safe code
    deactivate TSFront

    activate CodeRevFE
    Note right of CodeRevFE: Review:<br/>- Security (XSS)<br/>- Performance<br/>- Accessibility<br/>- Best practices
    CodeRevFE-->>MobileUX: ✓ Code approved
    deactivate CodeRevFE

    activate MobileUX
    Note right of MobileUX: Test responsive:<br/>- Mobile 320px<br/>- Tablet 768px<br/>- Desktop 1024px<br/>- Screenshots (Playwright)
    MobileUX-->>DebugFE: ✓ Responsive
    deactivate MobileUX

    activate DebugFE
    Note right of DebugFE: - Fix React warnings<br/>- Memory leaks<br/>- WebSocket logic<br/>- UI bugs
    DebugFE-->>Int: ✓ Frontend ready
    deactivate DebugFE

    %% PHASE 4: Integration
    Note over Int: PHASE 4: Integration & E2E (2.5h)

    activate Int
    Note right of Int: - Connect FE to BE<br/>- WebSocket connection<br/>- API integration<br/>- E2E tests<br/>- Cross-browser
    Int-->>Deploy: ✓ Integration complete
    deactivate Int

    %% PHASE 5: Deployment
    Note over Deploy,Prod: PHASE 5: Deployment (1.5h)

    activate Deploy
    Note right of Deploy: Hostinger SSH MCP:<br/>- Build assets<br/>- Deploy backend<br/>- Deploy frontend<br/>- Run migrations<br/>- Restart services
    Deploy->>Prod: Deploy to production
    deactivate Deploy

    activate Prod
    Note right of Prod: Smoke tests:<br/>- Health check<br/>- Test notification<br/>- WebSocket works<br/>- Monitor errors
    Prod-->>PO: ✓ Feature live!
    deactivate Prod

    Note over PO,Prod: Total Duration: 2-3 days (17.5h)